Pickle recipe

Ingredients

    		3 ½ cups water
    		1 ¼ cups white vinegar
    		1 tablespoon white sugar
    		1 tablespoon salt
    		4 cups cucumber spears
    		2 cloves garlic, whole
    		2 heads fresh dill


Boil water, salt, sugar and vinegar 

Let cool

Pour in jar with cucumber, dill and garlic 

Stick in refridgerator for about a week. 

They last around a month or two.
